Currently when one wants to add a custom message to an issue screen a customfield of type "message" must be used.  For example, on JAC the message "Test issues should be created in the Test Project" is shown on the create issue screen.

This is then displayed on the XML issue view, for example as {code} <customfield id="customfield_10301" key="com.atlassian.jira.toolkit:message"> {code}

Ideally, customfields should not be used for messages and some new feature should be implemented to add custom messages to issues.

